solutions.content:
```
DELETE FROM Person WHERE Id NOT IN (
    -- Use temperary table as a reference of what we want at the end
    SELECT tempId FROM (
        -- Rename the MIN(Id) column as 'tempID' so we can select in above query
        SELECT MIN(Id) AS tempId FROM Person GROUP BY Email
    )AS minID
);  
```

