**2) Optimised  - O(n)**

**The idea is based on complete mathematics. The recurrence relation can be formed as**

F(k) = 0 * Bk[0] + 1 * Bk[1] + ... + (n-1) * Bk[n-1]

F(k+1) = 0 * Bk+1[0] + 1 * Bk+1[1] + ... + (n-1) * Bk+1[n-1]
		   = 0 * Bk[n - 1] + 1 * Bk[0] + ... + (n -1) * Bk[n-2]

 F(k+1) - F(k) = Bk[0] + Bk[1] + .. Bk[n -2] - (n-1) * Bk[n-1]
					 = Bk[0] + Bk[1] + .. Bk[n -2] + Bk[n-1] - Bk[n-1] -(n-1) * Bk[n-1]  
					 = Bk[0] + Bk[1] + .. Bk[n -2] + Bk[n-1] - n*Bk[n-1]
					 = sum(0 to n - 1) - n * Bk[n - 1]

**Recurrence Relation so formed is**
 **F[k+1] = F[k] + sum(0 to n - 1) - n * Bk[n - 1];**


